summary: This document is an email chain from November 2021 between an FBI Special Agent and an unspecified recipient, likely a telecommunications company representative. The FBI agent is following up on a federal trial subpoena for phone records, noting that subscriber information for a specific phone number was missing from the initial production. The email highlights an active investigation into child exploitation and human trafficking.
